description:
This video teaches you how to build a compact and very fast quad dispenser unit for dispensing building materials. 

I plan on adding a few of these in the large storage room I'm building in my LP world for dispensing some of the main block types (cobble, dirt, sand, etc.).

I've timed the 4 dispensers releasing 16 blocks per second, or 960 blocks per minute. That is 4 blocks per second each, or 240 blocks per minute each. This is the same speed dispensers being activated by a rapid pulsar. 

Activating the Rapid4 Dispenser unit with a button causes it to run exactly 1 second, releasing exactly 16 blocks (4 each) every time.
